---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: UX Strategy & Design | Fox & Frame
description: UX strategy and product thinking for teams that need clearer decisions, stronger journeys, and measurable outcomes.
headExtras: |
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "@id": "https://foxandframe.design/#organization",
          "name": "Fox & Frame Studio",
          "url": "https://foxandframe.design/",
          "email": "hello@foxandframe.design",
          "logo": "https://foxandframe.design/assets/logo2LightBG.png"
        },
        {
          "@type": "WebSite",
          "name": "Fox & Frame Studio",
          "url": "https://foxandframe.design/",
          "publisher": {
            "@id": "https://foxandframe.design/#organization"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "ProfessionalService",
          "@id": "https://foxandframe.design/#organization",
          "name": "Fox & Frame Studio",
          "url": "https://foxandframe.design/",
          "email": "hello@foxandframe.design",
          "image": "https://foxandframe.design/assets/logo2LightBG.png",
          "areaServed": "United Kingdom",
          "knowsAbout": [
            "UX strategy",
            "Product design",
            "UX research",
            "Conversion experience design",
            "Digital consultancy"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  </script>
  <script data-goatcounter="https://foxandframe.goatcounter.com/count" async src="//gc.zgo.at/count.js"></script>
---

<main id="main">
  <header id="top" class="section section--chapter hero hero--centered">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-10 hero-copy">
          <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-2">UX strategy and product direction</p>
          <h1 class="display-5 fw-semibold lh-sm mb-3">Clarity before code.</h1>
          <p class="lead text-muted mb-4">I help teams define the right problems, align decision-makers, and ship clearer experiences that improve adoption and business performance.</p>
          <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-2 hero-cta">
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#work" data-goatcounter-click="hero-view-case-studies">View Case Studies</a>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg" href="#contact" data-goatcounter-click="hero-book-strategy-call">Book a Strategy Call</a>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-2 small text-muted">Consultancy-led engagements, with embedded support when it accelerates outcomes.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 hero-pills">
            <span class="pill"><i class="bi bi-check2-circle me-2"></i>Stakeholder alignment</span>
            <span class="pill"><i class="bi bi-check2-circle me-2"></i>Research-led decisions</span>
            <span class="pill"><i class="bi bi-check2-circle me-2"></i>Product strategy</span>
            <span class="pill"><i class="bi bi-check2-circle me-2"></i>Measurable outcomes</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="trust-strip" aria-label="Key assurances">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="trust-strip-inner">
        <div class="trust-item"><i class="bi bi-compass"></i><span>UX diagnostics</span></div>
        <div class="trust-item"><i class="bi bi-people"></i><span>Stakeholder facilitation</span></div>
        <div class="trust-item"><i class="bi bi-diagram-3"></i><span>Systems thinking</span></div>
        <div class="trust-item"><i class="bi bi-clipboard-data"></i><span>Measurement plans</span></div>
        <div class="trust-item"><i class="bi bi-display"></i><span>Execution support</span></div>
        <div class="trust-item"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i><span>UK-based</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="clarity-problem">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-3">Most teams do not have a design problem. They have a clarity problem.</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-3">Teams ship quickly, but priorities drift. Then time gets spent fixing avoidable friction across conversion, onboarding, and retention.</p>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">The work starts by defining what is actually broken, aligning the right people, and measuring what changes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="mini">
                <i class="bi bi-signpost-split"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold">Conflicting priorities</div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">Product, marketing, and leadership are misaligned.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="mini">
                <i class="bi bi-sliders"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold">Feature-first delivery</div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">Build decisions made before validation.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="mini">
                <i class="bi bi-life-preserver"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold">Support friction</div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">Users need help for tasks that should be easy.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="mini">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold">Rework loops</div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">Teams rebuild without fixing root causes.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-surface" id="work">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-end g-4 mb-4">
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-2">Selected case studies</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Each project highlights context, strategic decisions, and outcomes, not just final screens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5 text-lg-end">
          <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="/demos.html" data-goatcounter-click="view-all-case-studies">View all case studies</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="ffWorkCarousel" class="carousel slide ff-work-carousel" data-bs-ride="false" data-bs-touch="true">
        {% if work.items | length > 3 %}
          <div class="carousel-indicators ff-work-indicators">
            {% set slideIndex = 0 %}
            {% for project in work.items %}
              {% if loop.index0 % 3 == 0 %}
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#ffWorkCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="{{ slideIndex }}" {% if slideIndex == 0 %}class="active" aria-current="true"{% endif %} aria-label="Slide {{ slideIndex + 1 }}"></button>
                {% set slideIndex = slideIndex + 1 %}
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="carousel-inner">
          {% for project in work.items %}
            {% if loop.index0 % 3 == 0 %}
              <div class="carousel-item{% if loop.index0 == 0 %} active{% endif %}">
                <div class="row g-3">
            {% endif %}

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
              <a class="card card-soft work-card work-card-link h-100 hover-rise" href="/{{ project.url }}" data-goatcounter-click="case-study-view" aria-label="Read {{ project.title }} case study">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                  <div class="work-thumb mb-3">
                    {% if project.showcase and project.showcase.images and project.showcase.images[0] %}
                      <img src="/{{ project.showcase.images[0].src }}" alt="{{ project.showcase.images[0].alt }}" loading="lazy" />
                    {% endif %}
                  </div>
                  <div class="project-header">
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="h5 fw-semibold mb-2">{{ project.title }}</h3>
                      <p class="text-muted mb-0 work-card-subtitle">{{ project.subtitle }}</p>
                      <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3">
                        {% for t in project.tech %}
                          {% if loop.index <= 2 %}
                            <span class="chip chip-tech">{{ t }}</span>
                          {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                        {% for t in project.tags %}
                          {% if loop.first %}
                            <span class="chip">{{ t }}</span>
                          {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <hr class="my-3" />
                  <div class="result-pill">
                    <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i>
                    <span class="fw-semibold">Outcome</span>
                    <span class="text-muted work-card-outcome">{{ project.result }}</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>

            {% if loop.index0 % 3 == 2 or loop.last %}
                </div>
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>

        {% if work.items | length > 3 %}
          <button class="carousel-control-prev ff-work-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#ffWorkCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev" aria-label="Previous case studies">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <button class="carousel-control-next ff-work-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#ffWorkCarousel" data-bs-slide="next" aria-label="Next case studies">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-surface" id="what-you-get">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-end g-4 mb-4">
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-2">What I do</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Consultancy-led services for teams that need strategic clarity and practical delivery momentum.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5 text-lg-end">
          <span class="small text-muted">Strategy-led. Outcome-focused.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-3">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card card-soft h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="icon-circle mb-3"><i class="bi bi-search"></i></div>
              <h3 class="h5">UX diagnostics</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">Research, journey analysis, and friction mapping to identify the highest-impact opportunities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card card-soft h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="icon-circle mb-3"><i class="bi bi-diagram-2"></i></div>
              <h3 class="h5">Product and experience strategy</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">Experience strategy, IA, and roadmap alignment across product, design, and engineering.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card card-soft h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="icon-circle mb-3"><i class="bi bi-check2-square"></i></div>
              <h3 class="h5">Validated design and delivery</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">Prototypes, validation, and implementation support tied to clear success measures.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="#contact">Discuss your project</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="process">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-5">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-2">How I work</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">A structured approach that keeps strategy, design, and delivery aligned.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Discover</div>
                <div class="text-muted small">Gather business context, constraints, and goals.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Diagnose</div>
                <div class="text-muted small">Identify user friction and decision bottlenecks.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Define</div>
                <div class="text-muted small">Set strategy, principles, and success criteria.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Design</div>
                <div class="text-muted small">Prototype and shape experiences around evidence.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">5</div>
              <div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Validate</div>
                <div class="text-muted small">Test assumptions with users and stakeholders.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">6</div>
              <div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Measure</div>
                <div class="text-muted small">Track outcomes and guide continuous improvement.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="small text-muted mt-3 mb-0">Engagements are shaped around your stage, team capacity, and decision pace.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--chapter bg-surface" id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-end g-4 mb-4">
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-2">Engagement models</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Flexible ways to work together, from focused diagnostics to ongoing strategic support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-3">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="card pricing h-100">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
              <h3 class="h5 fw-semibold mb-1">UX Audit and Diagnostic</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-3">Focused engagement to uncover friction, align priorities, and define a practical roadmap.</p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>Heuristic and journey review</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>Stakeholder alignment session</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>Prioritised action plan</li>
              </ul>
              <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary w-100" href="#contact" data-goatcounter-click="contact-cta">Book a strategy call</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="card pricing featured h-100">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
              <div class="badge rounded-pill text-bg-primary mb-3" style="width: min-content;">CORE</div>
              <h3 class="h5 fw-semibold mb-1">UX Strategy Engagement</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-3">End-to-end discovery, strategy definition, and validated design direction for high-impact journeys.</p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>Research and behavioral analysis</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>IA and experience architecture</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>Measurement and rollout plan</li>
              </ul>
              <a class="btn btn-primary w-100" href="#contact" data-goatcounter-click="contact-cta">Book a strategy call</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="card pricing h-100">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
              <h3 class="h5 fw-semibold mb-1">Implementation Support</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-3">Design and build support aligned to validated strategy, with your team or as a delivery partner.</p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>Prototype to production support</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>Design system and UX governance</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2"></i>Iteration based on outcomes</li>
              </ul>
              <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary w-100" href="#contact" data-goatcounter-click="contact-cta">Discuss implementation</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="small text-muted mt-3 mb-0">Typical support includes SaaS products, lead-generation funnels, and other conversion-critical journeys.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-5 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-3">Senior UX thinking with practical delivery depth</h2>
          <p class="text-muted">I work at the intersection of UX strategy and execution, helping teams make better product decisions under real constraints. This site doubles as a working portfolio of how I think, lead, and deliver.</p>
          <div class="row g-3 mt-1">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="mini">
                <i class="bi bi-people"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold">Cross-functional leadership</div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">Aligning product, marketing, and delivery.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="mini">
                <i class="bi bi-kanban"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold">Decision frameworks</div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">Clear tradeoffs and prioritisation logic.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="mini">
                <i class="bi bi-mortarboard"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold">Mentoring and enablement</div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">Raising team capability through mentoring and clear standards.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="mini">
                <i class="bi bi-bar-chart"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="fw-semibold">Outcome ownership</div>
                  <div class="text-muted small">Tracking improvements beyond launch.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact" data-goatcounter-click="contact-cta">Book a strategy call</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="profile p-4 p-md-5">
            <h3 class="h5 fw-semibold mb-2">Who I work with</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">
              Teams and founders that need clarity, stronger UX direction, and a partner who can connect strategy to real delivery.
            </p>
            <div class="row g-2">
              <div class="col-6"><div class="tag">Scaling SaaS</div></div>
              <div class="col-6"><div class="tag">SMEs</div></div>
              <div class="col-6"><div class="tag">Founders</div></div>
              <div class="col-6"><div class="tag">Product teams</div></div>
              <div class="col-6"><div class="tag">Lead-gen teams</div></div>
              <div class="col-6"><div class="tag">Service businesses</div></div>
            </div>
            <hr class="my-4"/>
            <p class="small text-muted mb-0">
              Available for consultancy projects and selective implementation work.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-surface" id="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-end g-4 mb-4">
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-2">Outcomes and feedback</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Signals from client work focused on clarity, conversion quality, and user confidence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5 text-lg-end">
          <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="#contact" data-goatcounter-click="contact-cta">Start a conversation</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row g-3">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <figure class="card card-soft h-100 hover-rise">
            <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
              <div class="stars mb-3" aria-hidden="true">
                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
              </div>
              <blockquote class="mb-3">"The work moved us from ad-hoc decisions to a clear experience direction. We had better internal alignment and fewer customer pain points after launch."</blockquote>
              <figcaption class="small text-muted mb-0">- Product stakeholder, SaaS project</figcaption>
            </div>
          </figure>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <figure class="card card-soft h-100 hover-rise">
            <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
              <div class="stars mb-3" aria-hidden="true">
                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
              </div>
              <blockquote class="mb-3">"We got a strategy we could actually execute. The process made priorities obvious and improved conversion quality."</blockquote>
              <figcaption class="small text-muted mb-0">- Founder, lead-generation business</figcaption>
            </div>
          </figure>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <figure class="card card-soft h-100 hover-rise">
            <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
              <div class="stars mb-3" aria-hidden="true">
                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
              </div>
              <blockquote class="mb-3">"The diagnostic phase gave us the confidence to stop guessing and focus on the highest-impact user journeys first."</blockquote>
              <figcaption class="small text-muted mb-0">- Operations lead, SME team</figcaption>
            </div>
          </figure>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <figure class="card card-soft h-100 hover-rise">
            <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
              <div class="stars mb-3" aria-hidden="true">
                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
              </div>
              <blockquote class="mb-3">"Senior-level UX thinking plus practical delivery support made this feel like an extension of our internal team."</blockquote>
              <figcaption class="small text-muted mb-0">- Marketing and product team, growth-stage business</figcaption>
            </div>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="blog">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-end g-4 mb-4">
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-2">Thinking and insights</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Practical articles on UX leadership, decision-making, and product clarity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5 text-lg-end">
          <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="{{ site.mediumProfileUrl if mediumPosts and mediumPosts.length and site.mediumProfileUrl else '/blog/' }}" {% if mediumPosts and mediumPosts.length and site.mediumProfileUrl %}target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"{% endif %}>View all posts</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-3">
        {% if mediumPosts and mediumPosts.length %}
          {% for post in mediumPosts %}
            {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <a class="card card-soft h-100 hover-rise blog-card blog-card--link" href="{{ post.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                {% if post.thumbnail %}
                  <img src="{{ post.thumbnail }}" class="card-img-top blog-card__img" alt="{{ post.title }}" loading="lazy" />
                {% endif %}
                <div class="card-body">
                  <div class="small text-muted mb-2">{{ post.source }}{% if post.dateLabel %} • {{ post.dateLabel }}{% endif %}</div>
                  <h3 class="h5 mb-2">{{ post.title }}</h3>
                  {% if post.summary %}
                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">{{ post.summary }}</p>
                  {% endif %}
                  <span class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">Read on Medium</span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        {% else %}
          {% for post in collections.blog %}
            {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <a class="card card-soft h-100 hover-rise blog-card blog-card--link" href="{{ post.url }}">
                {% if post.data.thumbnail %}
                  <img src="{{ post.data.thumbnail | urlFor }}" class="card-img-top blog-card__img" alt="{{ post.data.thumbnailAlt }}" loading="lazy" />
                {% endif %}
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h3 class="h5 mb-2">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                  {% if post.data.summary %}
                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
                  {% endif %}
                  <span class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">Read article</span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-surface" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-5">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-2">FAQ</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Quick answers about consultancy, delivery, and fit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <div class="faq" role="list">
            <details class="faq-item" role="listitem" open>
              <summary class="faq-q">Can you support teams beyond short project phases?</summary>
              <div class="faq-a text-muted">
                Yes. I support both focused project work and longer engagements where ongoing UX direction is needed.
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq-item" role="listitem">
              <summary class="faq-q">Do you still take on implementation work?</summary>
              <div class="faq-a text-muted">
                Yes. Implementation is available where it supports a validated strategy. The goal is always outcomes, not just output.
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq-item" role="listitem">
              <summary class="faq-q">Can AI tools replace this process?</summary>
              <div class="faq-a text-muted">
                AI can speed up production. It does not replace stakeholder alignment, product judgement, or defining what should be built and how success is measured.
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq-item" role="listitem">
              <summary class="faq-q">What does a first engagement usually look like?</summary>
              <div class="faq-a text-muted">
                Most starts are a focused UX diagnostic. That gives both sides a clear view of priorities before moving into a longer strategy or delivery engagement.
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq-item" role="listitem">
              <summary class="faq-q">Is this suitable for side-project budgets?</summary>
              <div class="faq-a text-muted">
                Yes for the right scope. Smaller engagements are available for founders and SMEs that need high-value UX input without a full agency retainer.
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
          <p class="small text-muted mt-3 mb-0">If you are unsure where to start, a strategy call is the fastest way to scope the right next step.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--chapter" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-5 align-items-start">
        <div class="col-lg-5">
          <h2 class="h1 fw-semibold mb-2">Book a strategy call</h2>
          <p class="text-muted">Tell me what you are building, where the friction is, and what outcomes you need. I will come back with a clear recommendation on the next step.</p>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="d-flex gap-3 align-items-start mb-3">
              <div class="icon-circle"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i></div>
              <div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Based in South Yorkshire</div>
                <div class="text-muted">Working with UK teams and remote clients.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex gap-3 align-items-start mb-3">
              <div class="icon-circle"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i></div>
              <div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Email</div>
                <div class="text-muted">hello@foxandframe.design</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 callout">
              <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                <div class="callout-icon"><i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="h6 mb-1 fw-semibold">Quick note</h3>
                  <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                    If you include your current site, product, or funnel link, I can review context before replying.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <div class="card card-soft">
            <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
              <h3 class="h5 fw-semibold mb-3">Send a message</h3>
              <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mjgebrkq" method="post" class="row g-3" novalidate>
                <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New enquiry - Fox & Frame Studio" />
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <label class="form-label" for="name">Name</label>
                  <input class="form-control" id="name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <label class="form-label" for="business">Business name</label>
                  <input class="form-control" id="business" name="business" type="text" autocomplete="organization" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <label class="form-label" for="email">Email</label>
                  <input class="form-control" id="email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <label class="form-label" for="phone">Phone (optional)</label>
                  <input class="form-control" id="phone" name="phone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-12">
                  <label class="form-label" for="message">What do you need help with?</label>
                  <textarea class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                  <div class="form-text">
                    Helpful context: current digital setup, key friction points, and what success looks like.
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-2 align-items-sm-center justify-content-between">
                  <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" type="submit" onclick="goatcounter.count({path: '/contact-submit'})">Send message</button>
                  <span class="small text-muted">Reply within 48 hours (Mon to Fri)</span>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="small text-muted mt-3 mb-0">By submitting this form, you agree to our <a href="/privacy.html" class="link-secondary">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

